{"tid":424553,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【非打手】仲有無藉口留喺連登？","createTime":"2017-10-04T21:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T11:36:42.000Z","uid":144430,"like":15,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"571bfd2a62f495e0770f6d61ded42853a2d0dfb0","tid":424553,"uid":144430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T21:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/05/050133_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F05%2F050133_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=da7901fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/05/050138_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F05%2F050138_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=14482a54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信各位巴打都收到哩個訊息<br />\n（高登公關巴打辛苦了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n事不宜遲，等樓豬我帶大家參觀下新介面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先睇下介面<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/URX6GN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FURX6GN.png&h=06b4d546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白色嘅介面畀人一種煥然一新嘅感覺<br />\n整體操作順暢 <br />\n樓豬網速唔算快<br />\n 但介面Load得真係好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（Loading畫面啲公仔好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n唯一美中不足嘅係 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/Kbpmt8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FKbpmt8.png&h=5c543e05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下面嗰欄遮住咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（可能係我手機型號問題）<br />\n<br />\n以下為黑色介面<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/FU5OfI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FFU5OfI.png&h=75b21c49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一個字，型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講起介面點少得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講咁多 睇相<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/zfwKnC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FzfwKnC.png&h=261112ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好大。。。張圖<br />\n<br />\n選台介面應有盡有<br />\n埋嚟睇下有無心水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/9YpmjL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F9YpmjL.png&h=af5f6349&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，睇下留名同回帶系統<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/oyYnlG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FoyYnlG.png&h=26973f90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結：介面靚 系統正 但仍有進步空間[/quote]"},{"pid":"6ccb9687714abf684c467f29ad27a563d3f96027","tid":424553,"uid":144430,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T21:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好行喇 唔送喇<br />\n死返去高登啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e81b8fa6a7bcc12d354d0ec35e7eed687863e31","tid":424553,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T21:06:15.000Z","msg":"下？"},{"pid":"83c35ef5a23b611f6a2d830f76cd359274cb3b2b","tid":424553,"uid":144430,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T21:10:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好行喇 唔送喇<br />\n死返去高登啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無可否認 <br />\n連登熱鬧好多<br />\n高登一個台都係嗰班人傾<br />\n但係連登真係太多叫春Post<br />\n只要係女User(真假就唔知啦)叫春<br />\n成班MK 狗公就一窩蜂咁留言<br />\n表面關心 實情PM約炮<br />\n成為繼Scout、Tinder另一約炮神器"},{"pid":"c96320b30925b25b436193200c0556f98d83baf9","tid":424553,"uid":144430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T21:16:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好行喇 唔送喇<br />\n死返去高登啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無可否認 <br />\n連登熱鬧好多<br />\n高登一個台都係嗰班人傾<br />\n但係連登真係太多叫春Post<br />\n只要係女User(真假就唔知啦)叫春<br />\n成班MK 狗公就一窩蜂咁留言<br />\n表面關心 實情PM約炮<br />\n成為繼Scout、Tinder另一約炮神器</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多唔多低質Post好難講<br />\n（因為小弟並非高質，沒資格評論）<br />\n其實喺連登傾計段期間係開心嘅<br />\n同一眾巴打講好多關於自己嘅故事<br />\n我每一位都好用心去睇<br />\n逐個逐個回覆 好似同朋友傾計咁<br />\n覺得連登並無舊登講到咁差"},{"pid":"3b888105364921eaa5a95929b3ff054175b6ef59","tid":424553,"uid":144430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T21:21:10.000Z","msg":"但仍然有好多為鬧而鬧嘅留言<br />\n以我之前嘅Post而言為例<br />\n總係有啲搞事<br />\n喺成人台以外嘅Post放無碼相<br />\n同埋講一啲無任何內容可言嘅嘢"},{"pid":"213fc388c39b951aa06d716632fe9f2b4b191528","tid":424553,"uid":132488,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T21:27:45.000Z","msg":"肥絲 叫春 波台狗成班垃圾係到撚膠 廣告<br />\n太多原因"},{"pid":"ed7aa17a4786fc7cead0aac863da5f9aa3e52ab7","tid":424553,"uid":37979,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T21:28:21.000Z","msg":"樓主精神分裂?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0ca388794737ddb53b3a319af257abbd9e6cf5","tid":424553,"uid":144430,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T21:28:59.000Z","msg":"事先聲明<br />\n我唔係話高登無低質Post<br />\n亦唔係話連登無高質Post<br />\n每個地方都有好有唔好<br />\n尤其是&nbsp;連登比較多人上<br />\n良莠不齊少不免<br />\n但一上感情台見到成班&ldquo;雨果小子&rdquo;咁<br />\n個個喺道搵食<br />\n好心你地，搵食去第二道好唔好？"},{"pid":"7c9cddbd98a598e2e9ae3baf621bd1f3bfc97b31","tid":424553,"uid":144430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T21:34:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肥絲 叫春 波台狗成班垃圾係到撚膠 廣告<br />\n太多原因</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個肥絲真係狗養大名<br />\n一見到有post有錯字就捉人錯字都算<br />\n捉唔到錯字就捉人手粗口filter<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 習慣咗好難改"},{"pid":"99310189cb65289217794fb32f3df568b9a254dc","tid":424553,"uid":144430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T21:36:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主精神分裂?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為實會有人咁講<br />\n幫佢地講咗先"},{"pid":"9cb1af67c6d507689b78fbbaf7ff1ad1139d2d82","tid":424553,"uid":144430,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T21:36:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下咩<br />\n吓？定下載？"},{"pid":"562f9a84fa14128effc329cae16c389d88ddad0a","tid":424553,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T21:43:24.000Z","msg":"根本兩邊質素都差唔多㗎啦<br />\n申請要求一樣，文化一樣"},{"pid":"a81eb9080161552f40264e8f618474b4bf4caa96","tid":424553,"uid":49955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T21:45:25.000Z","msg":"翻高登了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dadebe0ebf5af67c8b73924610cb2710cacc2e0","tid":424553,"uid":52591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T21:51:16.000Z","msg":"回家"},{"pid":"7b3650bf0c831dac3669b8ad8000abfa84b08a02","tid":424553,"uid":42524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T22:02:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1cca09976fe15128482208e0d548821f71ddb679","tid":424553,"uid":144430,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T22:18:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔番去理由好多<br />\n1. 垃圾管理亂ban人<br />\n上高登超過5 6年都俾admin無理ban過4 5次，<br />\n解釋都無，唔岩聽就ban。<br />\n最撚過份講下邊間餐廳好食，打左餐廳個名出黎又ban<br />\n講下白份報又ban，講下咩意見都ban，有人投訴又ban<br />\n唔小心貼左J圖都ban<br />\n<br />\n依家所有都解封曬，乞人番去，<br />\n無可否認佢係